<plot>Diligent and hard-working Officer Sagar Chauhan's (Sunil Shetty) rising career in the secret services gets a set-back when he fails to rescue suicide-prone Meenal Patel (Raveena Tandon), the wife of wealthy and well-known Industrialist, Pratap Rai (Danny Denzongpa). To make matters worse Sagar had fallen in love with Meenal. A devastated Sagar is asked to proceed on sick leave, and goes out of the city. Once out of the city, he meets with the look-alike of Meenal, Namita Sharma (also Raveena Tandon), and old feelings re-surface. But thereafter he is thrust in a web of lies and deceit, as no one is who they claim they are.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?407838</url></doc>
